---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Axsetra KB | 安全、银行软件与数字资产"
  description="Axsetra KB 构建安全的网上银行平台 (AXSE)、VPS加固、无日志私人VPN解决方案，以及包括代币发行和加密交易所开发在内的区块链产品。"
  lang="zh"
>
  <Fragment slot="subtitle">个人 · 安全 · 金融 · 数字资产</Fragment>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-bg" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="hero-overlay" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="hero-content">
      <div class="container-fluid px-4 px-md-5">
        <div class="row align-items-center" style="min-height:100%;">
          <div class="col-12 col-lg-7 col-xl-6">
            <h1 class="hero-title axsetrakbfont titlecolor mb-2">Axsetra KB</h1>
            <h2 class="h4 subtitlecolor mb-3" style="letter-spacing:.02em;">个人 · 安全 · 金融 · 数字资产</h2>
            <p class="hero-lead subtitlecolor mb-4">
              Axsetra KB 构建安全的金融软件和注重隐私的基础设施：网上银行平台 (AXSE)、
              VPS加固、专属无日志VPN，以及代币和交易所的区块链解决方案。
            </p>
            <div class="d-flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              <a href="#services" class="btn btn-light px-4">浏览服务</a>
              <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-outline-light px-4">联系我们</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="ad-slot">广告位 - Google AdSense</div>

  <!-- SERVICES -->
  <section id="services" class="container py-5">
    <div class="row mb-4">
      <div class="col-lg-9">
        <h2 class="axsetrakbfont mb-2">服务</h2>
        <p class="text-muted mb-0">为银行、金融科技公司和私人客户提供安全设计的开发：网络平台、网上银行 (AXSE)、基础设施安全、私人VPN和区块链产品。</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row g-4">
      <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-xl-4">
        <div class="card service-card h-100">
          <div class="service-media service-media-icon"><div class="service-icon" aria-hidden="true">&#x1F310;</div></div>
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3 class="h5 card-title">安全网络平台与集成</h3>
            <p class="card-text text-muted">高端网站和多语言平台，集成Python满足复杂的商业需求。</p>
            <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm">详情</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-xl-4">
        <div class="card service-card h-100">
          <div class="service-media service-media-icon"><div class="service-icon" aria-hidden="true">&#x1F3E6;</div></div>
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3 class="h5 card-title">网上银行软件 (AXSE)</h3>
            <p class="card-text text-muted">面向银行和金融科技公司的生产就绪网上银行软件：账户、支付、安全、合规。</p>
            <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm">详情</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-xl-4">
        <div class="card service-card h-100">
          <div class="service-media service-media-icon"><div class="service-icon" aria-hidden="true">&#x1F510;</div></div>
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3 class="h5 card-title">VPS加固与基础设施安全</h3>
            <p class="card-text text-muted">加固的环境：隔离、加密、访问控制和安全运营。</p>
            <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm">详情</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-xl-4">
        <div class="card service-card h-100">
          <div class="service-media service-media-icon"><div class="service-icon" aria-hidden="true">&#x1F6E1;&#xFE0F;</div></div>
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3 class="h5 card-title">专属私人VPN（无日志）</h3>
            <p class="card-text text-muted">专属高速VPN，支持自定义出口国家。不与其他客户共享。反监控设计。</p>
            <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm">详情</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-xl-4">
        <div class="card service-card h-100">
          <div class="service-media service-media-icon"><div class="service-icon" aria-hidden="true">&#x1FA99;</div></div>
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3 class="h5 card-title">代币开发与发行</h3>
            <p class="card-text text-muted">在ETH、BNB Chain和Solana上创建和部署代币，提供发行支持和链上配置。</p>
            <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm">详情</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-xl-4">
        <div class="card service-card h-100">
          <div class="service-media service-media-icon"><div class="service-icon" aria-hidden="true">&#x1F501;</div></div>
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3 class="h5 card-title">加密交易所开发 (DEX/CEX)</h3>
            <p class="card-text text-muted">与AXSE集成或独立的交易所系统：交易、钱包、集成和安全后端逻辑。</p>
            <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm">详情</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-xl-4">
        <div class="card service-card h-100">
          <div class="service-media service-media-icon"><div class="service-icon" aria-hidden="true">&#x1F30D;</div></div>
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3 class="h5 card-title">隐私域名与网络身份配置</h3>
            <p class="card-text text-muted">增强隐私的域名和网络身份配置，减少暴露，具有司法管辖意识。</p>
            <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm">详情</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="ad-slot">广告位 - Google AdSense</div>

  <!-- CONTACT -->
  <section id="contact" class="container pb-5">
    <div class="card p-4 contact-card">
      <div class="row g-4 align-items-start">
        <div class="col-12 col-lg-5">
          <h2 class="axsetrakbfont mb-2">联系我们</h2>
          <p class="text-muted mb-3">描述您的需求（概括即可）。我们将回复安全架构方案和后续步骤。</p>
          <div class="small text-muted">
            邮箱: axsetrakb@proton.me
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-12 col-lg-7">
          <form id="contactForm" class="needs-validation" novalidate>
            <div class="row g-3">
              <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
                <label class="form-label" for="id_name">姓名</label>
                <input id="id_name" name="name" class="form-control" required maxlength="120" placeholder="您的姓名" autocomplete="name" />
                <div class="invalid-feedback">请输入您的姓名。</div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
                <label class="form-label" for="id_email">邮箱</label>
                <input id="id_email" name="email" type="email" class="form-control" required maxlength="180" placeholder="you@company.com" autocomplete="email" />
                <div class="invalid-feedback">请输入有效的邮箱。</div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-12">
                <label class="form-label" for="id_message">留言</label>
                <textarea id="id_message" name="message" class="form-control" rows="5" required maxlength="4000"
                  placeholder="告诉我们您想构建/保护什么，时间框架和关键限制。"
                  autocomplete="off"></textarea>
                <div class="invalid-feedback">请写一条简短的留言。</div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-12">
                <div class="d-flex flex-wrap gap-2 align-items-center">
                  <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary px-4">发送消息</button>
                  <small class="text-muted">我们将在快速审核后回复。</small>
                </div>
                <div class="mt-2">
                  <small class="text-muted">
                    重要：我们从 <strong>axsetrakb@proton.me</strong> 回复。
                    请将其添加到您的安全发件人列表，以免错过我们的回复。
                  </small>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="ad-slot">广告位 - Google AdSense</div>
</BaseLayout>
